# REVIEW.md — Per-Repo Adversarial Review Tuning

This file is read by `codedungeon code-review` at the start of every run. It overrides the defaults baked into the orchestrator and persona critics. Copy this template to your repo's root and uncomment / edit the sections you need.

`@` imports do NOT resolve inside this file — everything is pasted verbatim into persona prompts.

---

