## Nit Cap

<!--
IMPORTANT: In this pipeline, P2 findings BLOCK MERGE unless classified as design decisions.
The cap is about recall noise, NOT about letting nits pass silently.

Default: each persona caps at 3 P2 findings; total P2 across merged findings capped at 5.
Override here if your repo wants stricter or looser caps:

- Max P2 per review: 8
- Suppress nit details entirely (only summary count): no

To prevent specific P2 patterns from blocking, document them in § Repo-Specific Known Patterns
below — that is how the design-decision classifier learns to skip them.
-->

